---

<style>
  .home-container {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 4em auto 0 auto;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 18px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 32px 0 #1e293b18;
    padding: 2.5em 2em 2em 2em;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5em;
  }
  .home-title {
    font-size: 2.2em;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #1d4ed8;
    margin-bottom: 0.2em;
    text-align: center;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }
  .home-desc {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 1.15em;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 1em;
  }
  .home-link {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #1d4ed8;
    color: #fff;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.15em;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 0.8em 2em;
    text-decoration: none;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #1d4ed822;
    transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
    margin-top: 1em;
  }
  .home-link:hover {
    background: #3245ff;
    color: #fff;
  }
</style>

<Layout>
  <div class="home-container">
    <div class="home-title">Welcome to the NEWS2 Dashboard</div>
    <div class="home-desc">
      This app helps you view and score patients using the National Early Warning Score 2 (NEWS2) system.<br /><br />
      Click below to view all patients and their NEWS2 scores.
    </div>
    <a href="/news2" class="home-link">Go to NEWS2 Overview</a>
  </div>
</Layout>
